<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ juàn gù nǐ wǒ, zhǔ lián mǐn nǐ wǒ, zài shì shàng yī wú suǒ yǒu. zhǔ
 juàn gù nǐ wǒ, zhǔ lián mǐn nǐ wǒ, zài shì shàng wú chù kě guī. wǒ
 men de xīn dāng yǎng wàng tā, rèn dìng tā bì dài lǐng wǒ men. zǒu guò nà
 màn màn rén shēng zhī lù, jìn rù tā de ān xī.
 a! jì jū shēng yá, a! zhǔ yǐ tóng zài,
 zhè jí dào nà jí, zhǔ yǒng yuǎn shì wǒ men de shén!</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ juàn gù nǐ wǒ 迦南52</title>
<hymn_number>52</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>